{"tid":2454603,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：巴基斯坦總理確診　兩日前曾接種疫苗","createTime":"2021-03-20T11:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T11:09:31.000Z","uid":290404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a51fec3e709d99b6239ca094a81ef89dd4dc68da","tid":2454603,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦總理伊姆蘭汗確診新型肺炎，<strong>他兩日前曾經接種中國國藥集團生產的新冠疫苗</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n衛生部長表示，伊姆蘭汗正在家中自我隔離。<br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦近期的疫情有惡化跡象，新增確診個案上升。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581647-20210320.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581647-20210320.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDL3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=e899953c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581647-20210320.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c141319a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581647-20210320.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"1547e5d7004a5112c914abcfb86e93257b258705","tid":2454603,"uid":264121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:05:30.000Z","msg":"睇國家名就知有用安心出行<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32228a96102208bc8c64c896ac60ccb2d253fb2a","tid":2454603,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:09:31.000Z","msg":"巴雞爛坦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}